title: Merge branch 'master' into app_tour
message:
Merge branch 'master' into app_tour

* master: (27 commits)
  Fix some FAB behavior
  Fix time being displayed in UTC glitch
  Further clean up
  Clean up
  Modify ActionActivity to use GetUserActionsTask
  Modify GetUserActionsTask to accept action filtering
  Add circle image behind the action icon
  Add fetch action on new intent (if activity is already open)
  Finish up ActionActivity and notification interaction
  version bump
  simplifying code needed to pull user data from the api; since we're now loading this from the /api/users/ endpoint, there's no need for all the Listerners and extra callbacks from multiple http requests; this makes a lot of this code unnecessary
  logging lots of stuff for now
  correctly parse/include parent and child data
  WIP: still need to clean up code from MainActivity, CAtegoryFragment, and MyGoalsFragment
  WIP: still need to correctly parse api results
  initial work on a GetUserDataTask
  logging requests to the api for UserBehavior and UserAction data
  adding a sync parameter, so we have an option NOT to connect parent/child content before loading data.
  extract the user-selected content (and management of it) from the CompassApplication into a new UserData class
  set the Action's reference to it's parent Behavior
  ...
